Package: VICE
Type: Package
Title: calculate Variability in sIngle-Cell/nuclei RNAsEq data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rujia Dai
Maintainer: Rujia Dai <rujiadai@gmail.com>
Description: VICE is a tool for calculating gene-level variability in single-cell or single-nuclei RNAseq data by constructing pseudo-replicates.
